lausible encounters with 2I/Borisov, within 2 pc and\n30 kms$^{-1}$. These encounters' high relative speeds mean none are likely to\nbe the home of 2I/Borisov.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Nov 2019 16:44:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 19 Feb 2020 17:27:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-18"}
