tainable low level\nof SIT control. We illustrate our theoretical results with numerical\nsimulations, in the case of SIT mosquito control.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Nov 2019 21:42:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-30"}
