}}$ and $T_{\\mathrm{IC}}$. The observations are interpreted in\nterms of the appearance of a hidden gapped state below $T_{\\mathrm{el}}$ that\nhas so far eluded detection by structural analyses.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Nov 2019 15:07:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-11"}
